Interface RWikiObject

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    RWikiCurrentObject, RWikiHistoryObject
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RWikiCurrentObjectImpl, RWikiHistoryObjectImpl, RWikiObjectImpl

    public interface RWikiObject
extends Comparable
    The base object for a Wiki page, id, name, realm, permissions, revision, version, owner

      • copyTo

        void copyTo(RWikiObject rwo)
        Copy a RWikiObject into an existing RWiki Object This will copy the contents and settings of the RWiki Object into the supplied RWikiObject. The ID and the User will not be changed, everything else will be coppied. NB. THE GLOBAL NAME, AND REALM WILL NOT BE COPIED, and should be changed by the calling method.
